    • Constructor Detail

      • Attribute

        public Attribute(String name,
                 Collection<String> allowedValues,
                 String defaultValue)
        The definition of one supported attribute. If there is no fixed set of allowed values, use ALLOW_ALL_VALUES. Non-required attributes must have default values. Required dattributes should map to a default value of NO_DEFAULT_VALUE_BECAUSE_REQUIRED.
        Parameters:
        name - The attribute name.
        allowedValues - The collection of allowed values, or ALLOW_ALL_VALUES if there's no fixed set of allowed values.
        defaultValue - The default value, or NO_DEFAULT_VALUE_BECAUSE_REQUIRED if the attribute is required.
